{
  "texts": [
    "In this stage, the agent generates visualization and modeling codes (A3) and executes the codes to report and summarize insights (A4).",
    "Having multiple visualizations and modeling approaches, users could select visualizations to merge a linked view (H3) and interactively explore it (H4).",
    "It comprises the following two-step approach:• Visualization and insight generation: When the user selects an agent-proposed task or proposes a task themselves, the agent writes codes to complete the analysis.",
    "The agent needs to choose appropriate data modeling and visualization methods for each task and run the codes to complete the analysis.",
    "The agent then needs to generate the insights into a structured format."
  ]
}